Author: Miguel Rodriguez <miguel@bigbearengineering.com>
Date:   Mon Mar 16 09:29:31 2026 +0100

    package: sync demo/growth dashboards, strip demo-intercept for v0.2.0

    - demo/growth index.html updated to current Flotilla UI (dark mode, kanban,
      heartbeat dots, collapsible cards, all v0.2.0 features)
