      that code is bigbearengineering.com-only, not appropriate for customer installs
    - Removed setupForms() demo-intercept branch and showDemoIntercept/closeDemoIntercept
      from package main.js (mock status logic retained — controlled by is_demo config)
    - Added assets/ to demo/growth (previously missing entirely)
